data.description: This home was gut rehabbed in 2020. All new modern white cabinetry, SS appliances, granite countertops, beautiful hardwood floors.  There are 3 bedrooms on the main floor equipped with a bathroom featuring a spa-like Jacuzzi tub.  The basement holds the 4th bedroom, a laundry room, spacious open family room and another full bathroom with a walk-in tiled shower. Great backyard with plenty of space to enjoy a beautiful sunny day.  New privacy fence installed recently.
